divs: sighting details1. coming out of our garage. 2. looked up in the air when in our car. 3. a large star\ airplane. 4. seemed to move under intelligent power. 5. i love ufos, and knowing more about them, so i felt excited to see my very first ufo and didn't stop watching until i was 100% sure it was gone. 6. faded away.
Summary: Bright, some what pulsating orange light pretty low to the ground. Made 0 sound and after about 15 mins went up at an angle into the atmosphere and faded away.
